4. cs.CY (Computers and Society) - The paper discusses the use of simulated data for evaluating network analytics, which has implications for the societal impact of such technologies. 
5. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) - The paper mentions the potential application of the simulation model for generating data on Internet and cellular communications, which has implications for cryptography and security.
